kgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"a789339a56494ced8e926009f7676399a7b8baa1","tid":2308955,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:56:23.000Z","msg":"科技大學校長史維去年11月在校內舉行論壇期間，有內地生被指推跌黑衣人，遭人包圍「私了」。21歲科大男學生被指有份傷人，早前受審後遭裁判官鄭紀航裁定襲擊傷人罪成，判監9個半月。男生就定罪與刑期提出上訴，今於高等法院申請保釋，獲法官黃崇厚批准，可以<strong><span class=\"red\">現金2萬元與父親提供1萬元現金人事保釋，並須交出旅遊證件，不准離港，以及每周向警署報到3次。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n上訴人在科大工業工程系就讀四年級。裁判官鄭紀航裁決時指，他反複觀看42段新聞片及閉路電視片段後，循衣着、髮型、右腕手繩中間有金屬連接等六項特徵，再比對警方拘捕被告時拍攝的照片，根據面形、輪廊、鼻尖、眉毛、眼袋、頭髮鬢角等特徵極度相似，斷定是被告犯案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/BOPXBFUB55A2XLZY4WCEUEA23Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FBOPXBFUB55A2XLZY4WCEUEA23Y%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2d3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=8c26003b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FBOPXBFUB55A2XLZY4WCEUEA23Y%2F&h=3ae5cf50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/BOPXBFUB55A2XLZY4WCEUEA23Y/</a>"}}